+//!
+//! # Wildcard Catch-All Routes
+//!
+//! The router supports catch-all wildcard routes using two equivalent syntaxes:
+//!
+//! - `{*path}` - asterisk prefix syntax (recommended)
+//! - `{path:path}` - converter suffix syntax
+//!
